<SBODY>Liber 145.
27 WARRANTY <ENAMEX TYPE="EVENT.xlife">DEED</ENAMEX>.
This <ENAMEX TYPE="EVENT.xlife">Indenture</ENAMEX>.
Made this <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">Fifth
day of April
in the year
of our Lord one thousand eight hundred and Eighty nine</TIMEX> Between <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Edwin R. Cornwell</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Malvina</ENAMEX>
<ENAMEX TYPE="COREF">his</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="FAMILYMEMBER">wife</ENAMEX> of the <ENAMEX TYPE="LOCALE">Town of Freedom</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="LOCALE">County of Cattaraugus</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="LOCALE">State of New York</ENAMEX>
of the first part, and <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Frank Chapman</ENAMEX> of the same place
of the second part,
Witnesseth, That the said part of the first part, in consideration of the sum of <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">Three hundred and Twenty
Dollars</NUMEX>, (<NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">$320.00</NUMEX> to <ENAMEX TYPE="COREF">them</ENAMEX> duly paid, have sold, and by these Presents, do grant and convey to the said party of the second part, <ENAMEX TYPE="COREF">his</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="NONFAMILY">heirs</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="NONFAMILY">assigns</ENAMEX>,
ALL THAT <ENAMEX TYPE="VEHICLE">TRACTOR</ENAMEX> PARCEL OF LAND, situate in the ⌨own of <ENAMEX TYPE="LOCALE">Freedom County of Cattaraugus</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="LOCALE">State of New York</ENAMEX>
distinguished as follows: Being part of lot No 37 Town 6 <ENAMEX TYPE="LOCALE.notgpe">Range 3</ENAMEX>. Holland Companys Survey
Beginning at a point in the center of highway at the north west corner of <ENAMEX TYPE="TITLE">Mrs</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Mary Burlesons</ENAMEX>
land thence running South <NUMEX TYPE="QUANTITY">Twenty</NUMEX> degrees <NUMEX TYPE="QUANTITY">forty</NUMEX> minutes west <NUMEX TYPE="QUANTITY">three</NUMEX> chains thence westerly parallel 10
the highway <NUMEX TYPE="QUANTITY">one</NUMEX> chain thence north <NUMEX TYPE="QUANTITY">fifteen</NUMEX> degrees <NUMEX TYPE="QUANTITY">forty five</NUMEX> minutes east <NUMEX TYPE="QUANTITY">two</NUMEX> chains and <NUMEX TYPE="QUANTITY">ninety
Eight</NUMEX> links to the center of the highway thence along said highway south <NUMEX TYPE="QUANTITY">seventy one</NUMEX> degrees
<NUMEX TYPE="QUANTITY">thirty</NUMEX> minutes East <NUMEX TYPE="QUANTITY">one</NUMEX> chain <NUMEX TYPE="QUANTITY">Twenty five</NUMEX> links, to the place of beginning containing <NUMEX TYPE="QUANTITY">thirty
four one hundredths</NUMEX> of an acre of land be the same more or less,
Win the appurtenances and all the Estate, Title and Interest therein of the said parties of the first part. And the said
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Edwin R Cornwell</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Malvina</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="COREF">his</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="FAMILYMEMBER">wife</ENAMEX> parties of the first part
do -- hereby covenant and agree to and with the said party of the second part, <ENAMEX TYPE="COREF">his</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="NONFAMILY">heirs</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="NONFAMILY">assigns</ENAMEX>,
that the premises thus conveyed, in the quiet and peaceable possession of the said party of the second part, <ENAMEX TYPE="COREF">his</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="NONFAMILY">heirs</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="NONFAMILY">assigns</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="COREF">they</ENAMEX>
will forever WARRANT AND DEFEND against any person <ENAMEX TYPE="COREF">whomsoever</ENAMEX> lawfully claiming the same or any part thereof.
In <ENAMEX TYPE="NONFAMILY">Witness</ENAMEX> Whereoff, The parties of the first part, have hereunto set <ENAMEX TYPE="COREF">their</ENAMEX> hand and seal the <TIMEX TYPE="COREF.dat">day and year first above written</TIMEX>.
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">E R Cornwell</ENAMEX>
Sealed and Delivered in Presence of
[ L. S.
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Malvina Cornwell</ENAMEX>
[ L. S.]
<ENAMEX TYPE="LOCALE">STATE OF NEW YORK</ENAMEX>.
S T .
<ENAMEX TYPE="LOCALE">County of CATTARAUGUS</ENAMEX>
<ENAMEX TYPE="LOCALE">Town of Freedom</ENAMEX> ┃ On this <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">11th day of April in the year one thousand eight hundred and
Eighty Nine</TIMEX> before <ENAMEX TYPE="COREF">me</ENAMEX>, the subscriber, personally appeared <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Edwin R Cornwell</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Malvina</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="COREF">his</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="FAMILYMEMBER">wife</ENAMEX>
to <ENAMEX TYPE="COREF">me</ENAMEX> personally known to be the same persons described in and <ENAMEX TYPE="COREF">who</ENAMEX> executed the within
instrument, and severely acknowledged that <ENAMEX TYPE="COREF">they</ENAMEX> executed the same.
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Geo W. Haskell</ENAMEX>
<ENAMEX TYPE="OCCUPATION">Justice of the Peace</ENAMEX>
and, amid and compared with the only <TIMEX TYPE="DATE.non">12th__day of February</TIMEX>__is
<TIMEX TYPE="TIME">o'clock PM</TIMEX>.
▓▓▓▓▓
</SBODY>
</NBX>
